General.Name: New Zealand Coastal Seafoods Ltd
General.Description: New Zealand Coastal Seafoods Limited processes, distributes, and exports nutraceuticals, seafood products, and marine ingredients in New Zealand and internationally. It primarily offers dried ling maw, bulk ling fish maw, and bulk dried greenshell mussels; and nutraceutical ingredients, such as astaxanthin, oyster, seaweed, greenshell mussel, abalone, collagen, and ling maw products, as well as omega powder and marine oil. The company is based in Nedlands, Australia.
